metadata.name: Moment after sunset
metadata.description:
The last reflections of the setting sun outline the silhouette of the city and people enjoying the coming coolness. Their voices are echoed by the cries of seagulls circling over the waters of the Bosphorus. One more moment and the lights will start to turn on and fresh tart Turkish tea will be offered on the embankment.  

Artist: Veronika Naumova
Location: Istanbul 
3700*2500px
300dpi
